1)design and implement a class for an RPG character
think about
1.how and where to store data
   name  level maxHP maxMana baseRunSpeed runSpeed sword shield are all in Stat

    lvl,baseDamage, swordDamage,name  is in Sword
    lvl, baseDefense , shieldDefense,name,equip is in Shield

2.what operations are needed
    initiate , lvlUp , show , attack ,equipItem , unequipItem are in Stat

    initiate , showStat , lvlUp are in Sword and Shield.

3.how and where to compute information
    compute swordDamage and sword lvl in class sword
    compute shieldDamage and shield lvl in class shield

    compute runSpeed maxHP maxMana in Stat

